an_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis">特拉维斯</a>在即将到来的英国巡演中与食品回馈捐赠平台合作，发起“Eat The Beat”活动。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="723" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566"><b>特拉维斯分享单曲《Gaslight》并谈论新专辑《洛杉矶时报》：“美国如此沉浸在自己的历史中”</b></a></li></ul><p>乐队正在与 Bankuet 平台合作，为今年圣诞节使用食品银行的人们筹集资金，鼓励粉丝通过 Bankuet<a href="https://www.bankuet.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>捐款，并在结帐时勾选“Eat The Beat”框。</p><p>粉丝们还有机会在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-single-gaslight-and-talk-new-album-l-a-times-america-is-so-wrapped-in-their-own-history-3604566">12 月巡演</a>的每场演出中捐款，Bankuet 志愿者将在商品摊位工作。</p><p>主唱弗兰·希利 (Fran Healy) 表示：“我从小就很穷，所以我们与 Bankuet 联手，不仅帮助养活越来越多不得不依赖食品银行的人，还帮助那些面临取暖选择的低收入人群或者今年圣诞节吃东西。” </p><figure id="attachment_3815606" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3815606" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3815606" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="弗兰·希利（Fran Healy），特拉维斯乐队主唱" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Travis@2000