2">Bus</a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-new-single-raze-the-bar-featuring-coldplays-chris-martin-and-the-killers-brandon-flowers-3754948">Raze The Bar</a> 》。这是他们八年来的第一张专辑，并且<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-share-deluxe-version-of-l-a-times-featuring-10-extra-tracks-3799890">还在十月份推出了带有精简版的豪华版</a>。</p><p>专辑正式发行后不久，乐队透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-used-the-beatles-lady-madonna-piano-to-record-single-gaslight-3775958">《煤气灯下》中使用的钢琴与披头士乐队《麦当娜夫人》中使用的钢琴相同</a>。</p><p>为了支持专辑的发行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-announce-exclusive-busking-set-in-london-3775891">乐队于7月在伦敦街头进行了街头表演</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-surprise-fans-by-busking-in-glasgow-city-centre-on-a-vintage-double-decker-bus-3774801">此前还在格拉斯哥的一辆老式双层巴士上</a>进行了表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-join-with-food-bank-donation-platform-to-launch-eat-the-beat-campaign-3816618">Travis 联合食品银行捐赠平台发起“Eat The Beat”活动的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
